channel.title: Already bought domain, and forums, need a server
channel.description:
I have already bought a domain, and IP. Board forums, and then all of my developers for the server left me.
All i need is someone that knows how to code, and can make the server, and put it online for people to play.
Basically, If there's someone out there who has a nice server, and doesint have forums, or a domain. Contact me.
I'm Basically Giving one Away for free, but i'm Going to be the Web Developer/Co-Owner.
Thanks for reading, and make sure to contact me!
If you want to see the forums that i have made go to - *
